{"title":"十月，祖国！不仅仅是在十月","authors":["雷抒雁"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":10,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月，祖国！不仅仅是在十月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷抒雁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总是白鸽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱醒十月的第一个早晨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我知道，这是一个庄严的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从大兴安岭密林里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最小的山村"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衣履普通的村民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到西沙群岛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白浪簇拥的哨所"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"着装严整的士兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都会早早醒来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了这个日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擦拭得闪闪发光的铜钗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皮面在火堆上烤得紧绷绷的大鼓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以及弯曲如蛇的圆号"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都将以同一张乐谱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"演奏欢庆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给祖国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地，也不例外"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天然的色彩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早已编织出祥瑞的图案"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枫叶铺展红绸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金菊拥抱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点缀起硕大的五星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些善于歌唱的鸟儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像画眉、云雀、夜莺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甚至连跳跃在草丛间的蟋蟀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都一概地亮起歌喉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"表达欢乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜晚，焰火从天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"徐徐散落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂欢之后舞蹈也已停歇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有星群俯视大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华灯绽放，如不眠的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站立在空阔的广场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你会听见有一种声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"震撼心灵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是秋声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那不是苍凉的风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿过黄叶发出的凄厉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不是八月既望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤壁之下，舟子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悲怨的管箫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹奏的孤独"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我知道那是汉白玉的基座上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浮雕的历史发出的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些不曾写出名字的献身者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对梦想与光荣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发出的赞叹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月，生者与死者共有的季节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绵延的奋斗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是生长着的事业与情爱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是，祖国啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我日日夜夜挥汗如雨的祖国啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我年年月月美艳如玉的祖国啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月，又不仅仅是在十月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你让我们激动不已"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烟雨三月，在江南"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我醉心于柳丝后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你朦朦胧胧的面容"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当油菜的花朵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镀金大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我愿是一只小小的蜜蜂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿行在你的花丛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的长江，我的黄河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一遍遍歌唱过你的壮美"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱白帆如鸟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你的碧波里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"振翅飞翔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是，纵然是洪水泛滥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的浊浪你的愤怒你的泥泞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同样是我的歌我的激情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的赤裸的双脚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔驰在你的泥水里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我以赤裸的肩背"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扛起一袋袋泥沙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"垒筑意志与坚定"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一刻，和你的亲近"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使我想起祖国、人民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们共同的家园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共同的呼吸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共同的命运"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月，当然不只是在十月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即使大雪封门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泥炉旁，对一壶烈酒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我与李白共饮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陆游失约，披一袭斗篷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在南方，他正骑驴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑对雪里红梅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宽宽窄窄的板桥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深深浅浅的诗句"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国，诗意弥漫着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的每个季节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银杏树扇形叶片下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远缀满"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄金的果子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国，我分分秒秒的祖国啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿过城市，你以高楼的身影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你以汽笛的鸣叫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你以车水马龙的热闹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甚至以少女时尚衣裙的鲜艳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以小贩们嘈杂的吆喝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争斤论两讨价还价的世俗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我感受到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的心跳与活力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而在田野，无论是等待收割的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是刚刚插满绿秧的稻田"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发芽与落叶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开花与结果"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都很平常，一切的过程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都应和着你，祖国，你匀称的呼吸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄黄绿绿，阴阴晴晴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去去留留，来来往往"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有什么能使你的脚步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"停滞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一千年又一千年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从古老走向年轻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从印满绳纹的灰陶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一步步走向每秒百亿次的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"计算机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从龟板上艰难的刻字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和柔软的羊毫写下的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚劲笔锋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到键盘敲打出的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"块垒文章"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的方块字的中国啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你五千年的恬静创造"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，成了智慧疾速的闪回"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与跳动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉睡，或猛醒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摒弃，或张扬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"低吟，或长歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彷徨，或疾行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的祖国啊，你的一枝一叶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都牵动着我的情感"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牵动着我的歌唱和吟咏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牵动着我的神经"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我和考古学家一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深深发掘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻拂去历史灰尘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"探寻你既往的奥秘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和建筑工一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们层楼更上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"攀立在时代制高点上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞻望即将到来的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的世纪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熟悉而又陌生的祖国啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熟悉了的你的落后你的羸弱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的迟滞的步履"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天已变得陌生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陌生过的你的繁荣你的强大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的疾飞的超越"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天又变得这样熟悉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国，拥有你的每一年每一月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的幸福都难以诉说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是，十月，仍然是十月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个季节里的黄金"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使你变得辉煌、灿烂和芳香"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月的第一天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我会如此悠闲地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"躺在草坪上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"享受阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹过耳旁，送来欢笑、歌声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以及鼓乐的震响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桂花浓郁的气息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我感受到生活的芬芳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随手折断一枝草叶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在嘴里吸吮泥土和露珠的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清甜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朦胧的眼睛望着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白色云朵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在空中随意变幻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸽群掠过，清脆的哨声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诉说和平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我说：鸽子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请重新衔上这枝草叶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告诉世界"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一片希望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在东方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫中国！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}